{"tid":1829790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文當選後美國軍艦首穿台灣海峽","createTime":"2020-01-19T05:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:27:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b39e75c49970c916fdaf30c7492a9ebc20565cd4","tid":1829790,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"蔡英文當選後美國軍艦首穿台灣海峽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200117-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%BE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%E7%A9%BF%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200117-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2589%25A6%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B3%25BD&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=86aaae25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200117-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%BE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%E7%A9%BF%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>任何國家軍艦穿越台灣海峽都成為敏感事件。台灣國防部1月17日稱，美國一艘作戰艦16日根據一般航行任務從西南海域，由南向北經過台灣海峽，台灣軍方全程掌握，中方也表示密切關注並監視該艦。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據美國之音今天報道說，台灣大選後美艦首度穿越台海，中方表示密切監視。據台灣國防部1月17日稱，美國一艘作戰艦16日根據一般航行任務從西南海域，由南向北經過台灣海峽，台灣軍方全程掌握，中方也表示密切關注並監視該艦。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，這是在台灣總統蔡英文1月11日的台灣大選中以壓倒性優勢贏得連任後，美國軍艦首次穿越台灣海峽航行。在此之前，中國自製航母&ldquo;山東艦&rdquo;曾經兩度航行台灣海峽，台灣政府譴責此舉試圖影響選舉。<br />\n<br />\n據中國外交部發言人耿爽17日在例行記者會上表示，中方密切關注並且全程掌握美國軍艦過航台灣海峽的情況。據耿爽強調，台灣問題事關中國的主權和領土完整，是中美關係中最重要、最敏感的問題。&ldquo;我們敦促美方恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報的規定，慎重妥善地處理涉台問題，以免損害中美關係和台海的和平穩定。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">報道稱，美國海軍第七艦隊發言人凱利(Joe Keiley)表示，提康德羅加級(Ticonderoga-class)導彈巡洋艦夏洛號(USS Shiloh)是依據國際法例行通過台灣海峽。這位發言人還說，這項行動是展現美國致力於自由開放的印太區域。美國海軍會持續在國際法允許的任何地方飛行、航行與執行任務。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"986cf26d7fc391d62ef1facd7e98c2e5d170e5d8","tid":1829790,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c4aa9913918cefb134ed86b5cfc40107dc9c719","tid":1829790,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99e5e60d0b829a5cecde88e19300945cdeaa6bfd","tid":1829790,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faf967d9fb35d1d0a903c3a34be018e7b41e1670","tid":1829790,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72e4cdd081a89b47ff8f41fc94d285c32271ad63","tid":1829790,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd46ea5b6c218cc21f47f07a9cf2072a393ef9d5","tid":1829790,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">便衣警想屈西九影相學生搶槍</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1829251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1829251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u96ftcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu96ftcR.jpg&h=75a42d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">坐爆48都要7000蚊保釋<br />\n又屈搶槍 又私刑<br />\n無人講？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zu76z34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzu76z34.jpg&h=9d03f884&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ED13Chq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FED13Chq.jpg&h=21588f1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04aadb51d935153ab9b041323296e016c8d44f14","tid":1829790,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit